{"tid":2317903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宣美右膝蓋半脫臼狀態：跑不跑到一半脫臼了","createTime":"2020-12-09T02:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T06:30:20.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d5edd2bd0d7a1d2360fde936bf3f48dd2dbaafe4","tid":2317903,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:40:55.000Z","msg":"愛豆難當，練舞多年總會落下一身年輕球員，只是他們很少在粉絲面前表露出來而已。<br />\n<br />\n日前，Mnet新綜藝《奔跑之間》舉辦了製作發佈會，宣美、EXID Hani和Oh My Girl諟我、本月少女Chuu出席了活動，宣美就透露自己因為膝蓋傷無法跑步。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宣美稱：「我右腿膝蓋是半脫臼狀態，不太適合跑步。 其實我沒打算說出來，但最後跑步的時候膝蓋突然脫臼了，我也驚呆了。 幸好這檔節目不是專門講跑步的，而是各自按照自己的步伐奔走的內容，我就按照自己的速度進行就好了。 大家都出道蠻久了，加上經常練舞、跳舞，所以膝蓋都不怎麼好，我還蠻擔心的。 不過大家也很注重養生，吃了不少健康食品。 」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2fe1ae9a34bc338e017019761a57d83f/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132184-888153.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2fe1ae9a34bc338e017019761a57d83f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132184-888153.png&h=1530e3cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被稱為「南韓第一腿精」的宣美一雙美腿又細又長又直，不像那些過於骨感的「筷子腿」，她的腿部線條非常的勻稱，是一種很健康的美感。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_55af6378fd6a197ad3804728d2a79877/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132184-888150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_55af6378fd6a197ad3804728d2a79877%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132184-888150.png&h=2dc821a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過每次回歸時，粉絲們都會發現她的膝蓋又有淤青了，一看就是努力練舞的時候磕到的。 宣美真的在私下裡很努力，就是為了給粉絲們呈現一個更完美的舞台，腿上的這些傷疤也算是見證了她不平凡的經歷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_65ae6e8f823eb20c0e81c7ffe9e4429c/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132184-888151.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_65ae6e8f823eb20c0e81c7ffe9e4429c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132184-888151.png&h=d6e51054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_09d6954295b48d7ff0252be891ce34ae/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132184-888148.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_09d6954295b48d7ff0252be891ce34ae%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132184-888148.png&h=0ba45a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d7a8743b48b3a535e4485b2a3bb543db/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132184-888152.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d7a8743b48b3a535e4485b2a3bb543db%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132184-888152.png&h=6f89181a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18c1fea7782778bfd13318452aa9ae83aa429888","tid":2317903,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好中炎"},{"pid":"116bbf668adc307fc05c34a8eebb467396c02a51","tid":2317903,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66df065f2a68d08f89aaca262328cef1f675c84d","tid":2317903,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"斷十字韌帶？"},{"pid":"f4be2c5622b72a1176a74157b88e90975d12a25e","tid":2317903,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6baf65ade9987512c788a7a0b0af1d019e60818","tid":2317903,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T02:45:35.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 